=The Autumn Ballad=

2
00:00:19,273 --> 00:00:25,193
♪Winter clouds fill up the sky as the
geese leave behind a trail of sorrow♪

3
00:00:26,351 --> 00:00:32,281
♪I lean in front of the window,
gazing from afar♪

4
