♪As our eyes meet each other,
our longing is still there♪

7
00:00:48,513 --> 00:00:52,153
♪Mountains and seas apart,
waiting for the full moon♪

8
00:00:52,233 --> 00:00:55,873
♪All for our sweet encounter♪

9
